# Employee Attendance Management System

## Overview

The Employee Attendance Management System is a C++ application developed using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts to efficiently manage employee records and attendance data.

## Features

* Add employee records
* Update employee attendance
* View attendance records
* Search employee information
* Manage employee data efficiently

## Technologies Used

* C++
* Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

